OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy day ahead with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain and drizzle, this
OL,7,Fmost persistent through the morning.
OL,8,FDrier interludes expected into the
OL,9,Fafternoon, though remaining breezy all
OL,10,Fday. Feeling a little warmer than
OL,11,FSaturday.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry this evening and
OL,14,Fremaining cloudy overnight. With the
OL,15,Fadded breeze, this will hold
OL,16,Ftemperatures up leaving a frost-free
OL,17,Fnight to come.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
