OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FMostly dry to start, with some
OL,6,Fbrighter spells. Thicker cloud moving
OL,7,Fin from the west later with further
OL,8,Fspells of rain. Mild with lighter
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fon Tuesday with some patchy rain,
OL,13,Fbefore turning drier and brighter on
OL,14,FWednesday and Thursday. Lighter winds.
OL,15,FFeeling pleasant in the sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
